msgctxt "White hole"
msgid "Use the laser rifle to place it."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6944
msgctxt "Mercenary"
msgid "The Mercenary can fly in the air using their machine gun."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6945
msgctxt "Mercenary"
msgid ""
"They can also create a powerful bomb with their hammer that can be charged "
"by hitting it or with a laser rifle."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6949
msgctxt "Mercenary"
msgid ""
"Mercenary can also throw poison grenades that deal {int:NumDamagePoints} "
"damage point and prevent the infected from healing."
msgid_plural ""
"Mercenary can also throw poison grenades that deal {int:NumDamagePoints} "
"damage points and prevent the infected from healing."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6957
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "The Medic can protect humans with the hammer by giving them armor."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6958
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid ""
"Grenades with medicine give armor to everybody in their range, including "
"Heroes and the Medic themself."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6963
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "Tranqulizer rifle makes the infected fall asleep for {sec:Duration}."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6968
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid ""
"Laser rifle revives the infected, but at the cost of {int:Damage} hp and "
"armor."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6971
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "Medic also has a powerful shotgun that can knock back the infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6974
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid "The Hero has all standard weapons."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6975
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid ""
"The Hero has to find a flag only visible to them. Stand still to be pointed "
"towards it."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6976
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid ""
"The flag gifts a health point, {int:NumArmorGift} armor and full ammo to all "
"humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6978
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid ""
"It fully heals the Hero and it can grant a turret which you can place down "
"with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6979
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid ""
"The gift to all humans is only applied when the flag is surrounded by hearts "
"and armor."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6980
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid ""
"The Hero cannot be healed by a Medic, but it can withstand a hit from an "
"infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6981
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid ""
"The Hero can refresh the position of the flag by /rflag in survival mode."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6984
msgctxt "Engineer"
msgid "The Engineer can build walls with the hammer to block the infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6985
msgctxt "Engineer"
msgid "When an infected touches the wall, it dies."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6986
msgctxt "Engineer"
msgid ""
"The lifespan of a wall is {sec:LifeSpan}, and walls are limited to one per "
"player at the same time."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6991
msgctxt "Soldier"
msgid "The Soldier creates floating bombs with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6994
msgctxt "Soldier"
msgid "Each bomb can explode {int:NumBombs} time."
msgid_plural "Each bomb can explode {int:NumBombs} times."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:6998
msgid "Use the hammer to place the bomb and explode it multiple times."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7001
msgctxt "Ninja"
msgid ""
"The Ninja can throw flash grenades that can freeze the infected for three "
"seconds."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7006
msgctxt "Ninja"
msgid ""
"Their hammer is replaced with a katana, allowing them to dash "
"{int:NinjaJump} time before touching the ground."
msgid_plural ""
"Their hammer is replaced with a katana, allowing them to dash "
"{int:NinjaJump} times before touching the ground."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7012
msgid ""
"They also have a laser rifle that blinds the target for a short period of "
"time."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7013
msgid ""
"Ninja gets special targets. For killing a target, extra points and abilities "
"are awarded."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7017
msgctxt "Sniper"
msgid ""
"The Sniper can lock the position in mid-air for 15 seconds with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7019
msgctxt "Sniper"
msgid ""
"The locked position increases the Sniper's rifle damage from usual 10-13 to "
"30 damage points."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7021
msgctxt "Sniper"
msgid "They can also jump two times in the air."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7024
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid "The Scientist can pose floating mines with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7027
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid "Mines are limited to {int:NumMines} per player at the same time."
msgid_plural "Mines are limited to {int:NumMines} per player at the same time."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7030
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid "Scientist has also grenades that teleport them."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7031
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid ""
"A lucky Scientist devoted to killing can get a white hole that sucks the "
"infected in which can be placed with the laser rifle."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7035
msgctxt "Biologist"
msgid ""
"The Biologist has a shotgun with bouncing bullets and can create a spring "
"laser trap by shooting with the laser rifle."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7037
msgctxt "Biologist"
msgid ""
"They are also immune to continuous poison effect, and can stop it on "
"teammates with the Hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7041
msgctxt "Looper"
msgid ""
"The Looper has a laser wall that slows down the infected and a low-range "
"laser rifle with a high fire rate."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7043
msgctxt "Looper"
msgid "They can also jump two times in the air."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7046
msgctxt "Smoker"
msgid ""
"Smoker has a powerful hook that hurts humans and sucks their blood, "
"restoring the Smoker's health."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7048
msgctxt "Smoker"
msgid "It can also infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7051
msgctxt "Boomer"
msgid "The Boomer explodes when it attacks."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7052
msgctxt "Boomer"
msgid "All humans affected by the explosion become infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7053
msgctxt "Boomer"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7056
msgctxt "Hunter"
msgid ""
"The Hunter can jump two times in the air and has some resistance to knock-"
"backs."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7058
msgctxt "Hunter"
msgid "It can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7059
msgctxt "Hunter"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7062
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "Bat can jump endlessly in the air but it cannot infect humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7063
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "Instead, it can hammer humans to steal their health and heal itself."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7064
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "The hammer is also useful for healing the infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7065
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7068
msgctxt "Ghost"
msgid ""
"The Ghost is invisible until a human comes nearby, it takes damage, or it "
"uses the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7070
msgctxt "Ghost"
msgid "It can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7071
msgctxt "Ghost"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7074
msgctxt "Spider"
msgid ""
"The Spider has a web hook that automatically grabs any human touching it."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7075
msgctxt "Spider"
msgid "The web hook mode can be toggled by switching the weapon."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7076
msgctxt "Spider"
msgid ""
"In both modes the hook inflicts 1 damage point per second and can grab a "
"human for longer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7080
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid ""
"The Ghoul can devour anything that has died nearby, which makes it stronger, "
"faster and more resistant."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7082
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid ""
"It digests the fodder over time, going back to the normal state. Some "
"nourishment is also lost on death."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7084
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid "Ghoul can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7085
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:7088
msgctxt "Slug"
